    <item>
      <title>必和必拓以英美资源集团为目标，对矿业公司的报价为 390 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/bhp-proposed-offer-valuing-anglo-american-at-31-1-billion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[必和必拓集团有限公司 (BHP Group Ltd.) 提议收购英美资源集团 (Anglo American Plc)，该公司对这家规模较小的矿商的估值为 311 亿英镑（合 388 亿美元），这笔交易将使合并后公司的铜产量远远超过其竞争对手，同时引发该行业超过十年。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/bhp-proposed-offer-valuing-anglo-american-at-31-1-billion</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 06:48:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于发动机问题，威兹航空缩小了全年利润目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/wizz-air-narrows-full-year-profit-guidance-amid-engine-issues</link>
      <description><![CDATA[威兹航空控股有限公司 (Wizz Air Holdings Plc) 缩小了全年净利润指引，因为这家廉价航空公司因部分空客 SE 喷气式飞机的发动机问题而面临飞机停飞的局面。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-25/wizz-air-narrows-full-year-profit-guidance-amid-engine-issues</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 06:45:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
